INTRODUCING
PERSONAL STYLING
DEAN ALEXANDRA
LONDON,UK

Dear %%PC Name%%,

I'd like to personally introduce myself as your new Personal Stylist. As a Private Client, you're in the highest tier of our Access loyalty programme and can enjoy a personal shopping experience tailored to you.

Let me know how you'd prefer to keep in touch: I can contact you via WhatsApp, phone or email - whichever works best for you.

You can also find out more about all your exclusive Private Client benefits below.
Personalized Edits
Receive personalized product edits of the latest pieces from the brands you love, and the ones we think you'd like to get to know. Curated just for you.
Fashion Concierge
Can't find what you re looking for on FAREFTCH? Fashion Concierge can help you track down this seasons most exclusive pieces. Tell me what you re looking for and we'll handle the rest.
Exclusive Designers
As a Private Client, you'll receive access to exclusive designers, available on desktop and in our VIP App. Simply log into your FARFETCH account and look for the exclusive designer tab.
Priority Customer Care
You're our number one priority, which means you'll always have first access to sale, managed returns by your stylist, and expedited customer care.
You can also enjoy access to dedicated Private Client content. Just let me know your Instagram handle and I will add you. Then simply follow @Farfetch on Instagram to enjoy exclusive content.
Discover Your Benefits
Sound interesting? Let me know how you'd prefer to keep in touch: I can contact you via WhatsApp, phone or email whichever works best for you.
Until next time,
Stylist Name
Private Client Stylist
